  <concept id="concept_zvy_c3c_tbb">
    <title>Implement a Conversation App</title>
    <prolog>
      <metadata>
        <othermeta name="solution" content="Experience Manager" />
      </metadata>
    </prolog>
    <conbody>
      <p>You implement all conversation Apps using the same basic procedure. To implement a
        conversation App: </p>
      <ol id="ol_sc1_t4j_tbb">
        <li>Embed a core App. For information on how to embed a core App, see <xref
            href="c_using_livefyre.js_to_create_customize_and_use_apps_on_your_site.dita#c_using_livefyre.js_to_create_customize_and_use_apps_on_your_site"
          />.</li>
        <li>Create authentication tokens to use to authenticate users for an App using App Objects.
          Most Apps use the following objects:<ul id="ul_xkn_gqj_tbb"><li>NetworkConfig Object, see <xref href="c_networkconfig_object.dita#c_networkconfig_object"/></li><li>ConvConfig Object, see <xref href="c_convconfig_object.dita#c_convconfig_object"/></li><li>CollectionMeta Object, see <xref href="c_collectionmeta_object.dita#c_collectionmeta_object"
              /></li></ul></li>
        <li>Add an Event Handler. See <xref
            href="c_adding_an_event_handler.dita#c_adding_an_event_handler"/>.</li>
        <li>Build Server-side Tokens.<!--Need reference when it exists--></li>
        <li>Some Apps require additional, or slightly different implementations. For examples and
          App-specific implementation details, see the following App-specific integration
            information:<ul id="ul_ahv_cpj_tbb"><li>Comments, see <xref href="#concept_twr_xyd_tbb" format="dita" /></li><li>Chat, see <xref href="c_chat_integration.dita#c_chat_integration"/></li><li>Reviews, see <xref href="c_reviews_integration.dita#c_reviews_integration"/></li><li>Liveblog, see <xref href="c_live_blog_integration.dita#c_live_blog_integration"/></li><li>Sidenotes, see <xref href="r_sidenotes_integration.dita#r_sidenotes_integration"/></li></ul></li>
      </ol>
    </conbody>
  </concept>
</dita>